u Hamed, 35, was killed on January 14, 2025, after being shot in Ramla. She was transported to Kaplan Hospital in Rehovot, where she was pronounced dead. Police opened an investigation into the incident and arrested three suspects.","review_status":"flagged_for_review","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2025-01-01_2025-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2025-01-01_2025-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":313}